{
  "stem": "9168.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he-- and I felt so close to him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I felt especially close to him, and maybe in a protective way, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because it was difficult for him with this kind of father that we had.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, between my brother and me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my-- we were just sisters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember anything particularly joyous about our [LAUGHS] relationship as we grew up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that point, I-- I went into that school at 140 words per minute, when other students who were going into the court reporting course may have not had the push behind them that I had with this high school teacher.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After three months, I was writing 175 words a minute.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We also had all of the business courses that went along with the-- the manual skill of writing shorthand at very high speed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to reach 200 words a minute on different kinds of tests-- court-- that would be found in the courtroom testimony-- jury, charge, and literary.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It seemed as though by the time I was at 175 words per minute-- and we had a heavy medical terminology schedule in that school-- that I just had to go on-- had to find the way.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was-- it seems as I-- as though-- I remember $30 a month it cost to go in and out on the train.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And every three month period was $90 a month more, which was a great sum of money to my family at that time-- and then the tuition at the school.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This worried me all the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I have to get through this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I've got to do this faster, because of that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So my mother got the money, and we extended it for another three months.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
